The installation binaries can be downloaded from:

https://www.consul.io/downloads.html

It contains packages for:

1. Mac OS X
2. Linux
3. Solaris
4. Free BSD
5. Windows


Consul tools can be downloaded from:

https://www.consul.io/downloads_tools.html

1. Envconsul - https://github.com/hashicorp/envconsul
2. Consul Replicate - https://github.com/hashicorp/consul-replicate
3. Consul Template - https://github.com/hashicorp/consul-template
4. Consul Migrate - https://github.com/hashicorp/consul-migrate


